{"tid":1766579,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【再爆警謊】消防紀錄揭11.18人叠人66傷 警拖逾2小時才分流 逾半先送警署","createTime":"2019-12-02T16:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T03:08:35.000Z","uid":325840,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"2d30fb8e99b72d5774983a498b9f23c345cef778","tid":1766579,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"11月18日大批市民在油尖旺一帶聚集，聲援理大抗爭者，部份人在油麻地遭警方圍捕，其間更觸發「人叠人」。《蘋果》接獲一份相信是消防處內部的事故訊息紀錄，顯示意外當晚有多達66名傷者，包括16名紅色、9名黃色及41名綠色。消防處一度向警方提出，安排旅遊巴運送較輕傷的41名綠色傷者，惟警方回覆指傷者要先到警署，最終僅有31名傷者由意外現場直接送院，意味可能有逾半（35名）傷者未獲即時送院。消息人士又指，警方在事發後2.5小時，才准消防員分流傷者，但已錯過急救的黃金時間，嚴重延誤救援。<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191203&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60335028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191203%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60335028&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=3b10de55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191203%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60335028&h=67091ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191203&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60335028</a>"},{"pid":"3eda4292f12ad09626e12e9ddc0c4840dfba5717","tid":1766579,"uid":49202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:39:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4b8bd1ea3affa8d0154764467d5541c81b4d5ea","tid":1766579,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈] 時代革命由生活開始：黃色商圈已降臨（劉細良）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0321ec7e40e172d284cb100f5b012f046135006b","tid":1766579,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets