r />\n而醫院管理局早前亦已作出澄清指：「根據紀錄，公立醫院在該日接收的傷者中，並沒有死亡個案。」<br />\n<br />\n*****<br />\nCertain online reports accuse that a Police vehicle was involved in a fatal traffic accident during a violent incident in Yau Ma Tei last Tuesday (19 November). The Police clarify that this is false. <br />\n<br />\nIn the small hours of Tuesday, the Police deployed a vehicle to handle the chaos in Yau Ma Tei but it did not bump into anyone, let alone causing a fatal traffic accident. The Police express regret over this false rumour.<br />\n<br />\nThe Hospital Authority have clarified: &ldquo;According to our records, there is no death resulting from the cases of injuries received by public hospitals that day.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局澄清 Facebook 連結：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1572622596340601/posts/2489884237947761?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1572622596340601%2Fposts%2F2489884237947761%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=a17e74da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1572622596340601/posts/2489884237947761?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04M03xx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04M03xx.jpg&h=08045804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨係講架車囉"},{"pid":"5d65ff954fae784eb02acafe7fce7941ea5a294a","tid":1766579,"uid":196281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T17:14:13.000Z","msg":"查警謊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea013924cf193058cbdf247bc74620a914dd562","tid":1766579,"uid":53904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95d8616eeb7fa34f7cb614cc33ac8bb35285cfc2","tid":1766579,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201